rComments: Before choosing him this semester, i came on here to look at the review and saw a few bad ones. i'm usually a A+ student, so I told myself that maybe, those review werent accurate. I took this class to boost my gpa and I regretted it. Exams are long, tricky with way too many essay questions, and you dont have much time. Its really interesting tho
